<p>There is this lovely thing in yoga called &#8220;The art of starting over&#8221; from wherever you are, you just start over. Small goals (30 seconds) and of course not beating yourself up about the fact that you can&#8217;t sit still for 2 minutes (because you can start over) will eventually get you there.</p>
